{"tid":1383114,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"［策略討論］獻策更多淋熄蛋蛋","createTime":"2019-07-29T15:32:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-01T10:45:42.000Z","uid":266273,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"4a39986bf4bc3a11f917d711e47c8bf3cc48b426","tid":1383114,"uid":266273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T15:32:47.000Z","msg":"第一次開po<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />希望幫到少少呢場運動，關於淋熄蛋蛋<br />\n<br />\n早前聽過煙霧隊用雪糕筒淋熄蛋蛋，覺得好神奇，但未知實際執行係點，始終發夢唔喺最前線<br />\n岩先睇到呢條片，第一個問題諗：<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>有無更快方法</strong></span></span>！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zz8D3Ti.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fzz8D3Ti.png&h=87ba77fc&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5duzCdj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5duzCdj.png&h=5c510a3c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kDAKZrE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkDAKZrE.png&h=d943a750&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SBqbErF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSBqbErF.png&h=50fb78df&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Uso8GE1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUso8GE1.png&h=e5de592e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://touch.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=2397446087181093&amp;id=1683158261943216&amp;preview_rid=2397460813846287\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftouch.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D2397446087181093%26id%3D1683158261943216%26preview_rid%3D2397460813846287&d=BhuSHdI33QWLqsaIYsxmJVtf78QfJQp2bpA%2BRTfa5cI%3D&h=67dfb50d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://touch.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=2397446087181093&amp;id=1683158261943216&amp;preview_rid=2397460813846287</a><br />\n<br />\n忽發奇想：倒轉個筒，封一封底，倒水落筒，一野cup落去係咪會再快D熄？<br />\n<br />\n此Po旨在拋磚引玉，希望巴絲都可以講下自己意見。如果呢個方法work，將大大提升效率。尤其依加D狗好中意一射射幾粒咁射，D過期蛋又嗆過之前，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>效率決定一切</strong></span></span>！"},{"pid":"969145a00dee14f53250929ba16912b33bcec70f","tid":1383114,"uid":201374,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T15:33:53.000Z","msg":"當日現場冇咁多水"},{"pid":"fc9d0138f17ba2ae634650d5c46ff6ce542d150d","tid":1383114,"uid":65210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T18:23:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7213eaf1373bd5a241b32f0cc837116ae030fbde","tid":1383114,"uid":292980,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T18:39:54.000Z","msg":"開街井"},{"pid":"c5fbcec08145f529d84fca979f1332a445ba2212","tid":1383114,"uid":266273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7213eaf1373bd5a241b32f0cc837116ae030fbde","tid":1383114,"uid":292980,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T18:39:54.000Z","msg":"開街井"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T10:33:28.000Z","msg":"發夢喺上環站有見到，但無人用，都唔識用，係咪要有喉？"},{"pid":"a22c43f83a895aabf195047f88e858300b4dc959","tid":1383114,"uid":292980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T10:38:48.000Z","msg":"沒人有工具開制"},{"pid":"90b94e1c6c59654c50b0278701ff39b7e5c37ded","tid":1383114,"uid":257422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T10:40:04.000Z","msg":"#我係香港人 <br />\n#我會參與8月5日三罷 <br />\n#罷工罷市罷課"},{"pid":"68653409f2b8e9593239d688208ea6203391e79d","tid":1383114,"uid":74063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T10:46:42.000Z","msg":"滅火毯點睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}